| purpose = Through this treaty, Guatemala gave the education of the Guatemalan people to the regular orders of the [[Catholic Church]], committed to respect the ecclesiastical properties and monasteries, authorized mandatory tithing and allowed the bishops to censor what was published in the country. {{sfn | Aycinena | 1854 | p = 2-16}} 
